(In reply to Kubilay Kocak from comment #25)
I strenuously disagree. I was having the same issue (unreported) on Freebsd-12.3. However, downgrading go to 1.17 using pkg, and then rebuilding gitea fixed the issue. I believe gitea 1.16.5 fixes the reported issues because they are related from the 23 Mar upgrade of go to 1.18 within the ports tree. The gitea 1.16.5 changelog you referenced makes heavy mention of all the work to enable using go 1.18.

(In reply to Namkhai B. from comment #16)

@Namkhai, what version of go are you running that is successfully running gitea 1.16.4?

(In reply to Florian Smeets from comment #18)

@Florian, what version of go are you running that is successfully running gitea 1.16.4?

(In reply to Dan Langille from comment #21)

@Dan, can you try reverting go to 1.17 to see if that also fixes your issue?

